3. AUTHORITY FLOW MODEL
Authority flows:

Ring 0 → Ring 1 (Direct Sovereign Inheritance)

Ring 1 → Ministries (Delegated Authority)

Ministries → Chapters (Operational Authority)

Chapters → Task Forces (Conditional Authority)

Constraints:

No reverse authority flow

No lateral escalation

All authority must trace to Ring 0

Ethical & dignity invariants override all

